The Lake Poets is one man from Sunderland called Martin Longstaff. Martin makes honest, haunting &amp; moving Acoustic/IndieFolk music.

Despite only forming mid 2010, The Lake Poets has seen Martin already share the stage with not only some of the North East's best musicians &amp; groups, but also some of the cream of the U.K and U.S. Indie/Folk/Acoustic scene. By combining heartfelt &amp; haunting lyrics with an astonishing voice The Lake Poets have quickly amassed a legion of fans in a short space of time around the North East region, as well as further a field.

